to serve us tea and cookies.

492
00:19:12,930 --> 00:19:14,160
Hazamada: Mm-hmm.

493
00:19:14,200 --> 00:19:16,160
Koichi: I wanna go back
as soon as we can.

494
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:17,500
Hazamada: Me, too.
Today kicked ass!

495
00:19:17,530 --> 00:19:19,800
